%% User flow: pull policy documents. Diagrams-as-code: edit this, then re-render.
flowchart TD
  A[Enter carrier + email + password] --> B[Log in via Browserbase]
  B -->|bad creds / captcha / timeout| X[Show error]
  B --> C{MFA required?}
  C -->|no, trusted session| E[Fetch documents]
  C -->|yes| D[Code sent to SMS, user enters it]
  D --> E
  E --> F[Render documents + download]

%% Core assumptions:
%%  1. Login is by email, not User ID
%%  2. If MFA, the code goes to SMS (auto-picked)
%%  3. Documents live at a fixed URL and come back as PDFs
%%  4. One policy per account
